Title: Lupin III vs. Detective Conan
Writer: Monkey Punch (characters), Gosho Aoyama (characters), Atsushi Maekawa (script)
Actors: Kan'ichi Kurita, Minami Takayama, Kiyoshi Kobayashi, Wakana Yamazaki
Plot: When a queen and prince in a hunting accident, it's up to Conan to solve the case, while in the meantime Lupin's got his eyes on the Queen's Crown.
